SC06 will host a conference reception for all technical program attendees at Busch Gardens Tampa Bay. Get set to explore wildlife, wild rides, and live shows in the Timbuktu and Congo areas. Take the SheiKra challenge, America's only dive coaster, which takes you 200 feet up then hurtles you 90 degrees straight down. Or ride a raft through the white waters of the Congo.Buses will pick up attendees at the Tampa Convention Center and drop attendees off at Busch Gardens. After the reception, buses will return attendees to their hotels and to Convention Center. For those attendees who wish to drive to Busch Gardens, simply follow the Special Events signs that will direct you to the parking area for the SC06 event.Attendees will be required to wear technical program badges throughout the reception. Badges may be checke at any time.